OL,3,GPRESWATCHCBBC Newsline fails to appear
OL,4,Cat breakfast
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe 6.25am and 6.55am editions of BBC
OL,7,FNewsline failed to make it to air this
OL,8,Fmorning.
OL,10,FThe bulletins were replaced by a BBC
OL,11,FNews Northern Ireland-branded
OL,12,Ftext-based filler mechanism, showing
OL,13,Fheadlines and links to articles on the
OL,14,FBBC News Northern Ireland website.
OL,16,FA similar mechanism can be seen on the
OL,17,FBBC News channel in the UK, in place of
OL,18,Fad breaks shown on the international
OL,19,Fversion of the channel.
OL,23,EPub: 09-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
