OL,3,GPRESWATCHCBBC Newsline fails to appear
OL,4,Cat breakfast
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe BBC One Northern Ireland announcer
OL,7,Fprovided a verbal apology over the
OL,8,Ffiller graphic.
OL,10,FIt's unclear why the two early morning
OL,11,FNewsline bulletins weren't broadcast,
OL,12,Fbut normal service resumed at 7.30am,
OL,13,Fwith Kerry Thompson presenting from
OL,14,FStudio B.
